Use the correct output path (new designer)

In many tenants the Adaptive Card stepâ€™s output is nested like:

outputs('Post_adaptive_card_and_wait_for_a_response')?['body']?['data']?['action']


So use this exact Condition expression:

equals(
  coalesce(
    outputs('Post_adaptive_card_and_wait_for_a_response')?['body']?['data']?['action'],
    outputs('Post_adaptive_card_and_wait_for_a_response')?['data']?['action'],
    outputs('Post_adaptive_card_and_wait_for_a_response')?['body']?['submitActionId'],
    outputs('Post_adaptive_card_and_wait_for_a_response')?['submitActionId']
  ),
  'assignToMe'
)



